OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLife 'completely changed'  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter fall - Hanrif        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FKureishi                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Novelist Hanif Kureishi has spoken of  
OL,6, coming "face to face with death" after 
OL,7, a fall left him paralysed last year.   
OL,9,FThe My Beautiful Launderette author    
OL,10,Ffainted and fell on his head while on  
OL,11,Fholiday in Rome on Boxing Day.         
OL,13,FSpeaking from a clinic outside the     
OL,14,FItalian capital, he said losing the use
OL,15,Fof his arms, hands and legs has been   
OL,16,F"illuminating as well as terrible".    
OL,18,FMr Kureishi said the incident has left 
OL,19,Fhim feeling "like a piece of meat".    
